ome\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being fortunate enough to travel the world doing what I love, seeing new places and meeting new people and sports heroes, motivates me a lot.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"new places\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"new people\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"sports heroes\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most important thing every young swimmer should realise is that nothing is impossible.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most important thing\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"every young swimmer\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They only need to believe and be prepared to put in the long and hard hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the long and hard hours\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on missing qualification for the 200m breaststroke in Rio, Smith was typically upbeat about one of the biggest setbacks in her professional career.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999712256278026, \"rank\": 2.877520016558025e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"missing qualification\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m breaststroke\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest setbacks\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"her professional career\", \"from\": 1057, 